item.title: A Washed-up Nerd
item.description: This website is an aggregation of learning resources mined from open internet for Developers, IELTS test takers. It also posts helpful informatiom to regional poets and writers from 70's, 80's and 90's who are novice in computers but would like to host their stories and poems in hindi, telugu, tamil or other langauges to on personal websites.
